extends layout

block content
  
  div.row-fluid.rfcx-row-gradient.rfcx-row.rfcx-row-about-1.rfcx-row-about-1-1
    div.span12
      p.roadgeek.rfcx-header= "Finally, trees that can talk."
      p.rfcx-body
        span
          | <em>Rainforest Connection</em> uses up-cycled mobile technology to monitor and protect remote forests in real-time.
  div.row-fluid.rfcx-row.rfcx-row-about-1.rfcx-row-about-1-2
    div.span4
      p.roadgeek.rfcx-header.italic
        | &ldquo;If a tree falls
        br
        | <span style="position:relative;left:75px;">in the forest...&rdquo;</span>
      p.rfcx-body
        span.italic
          | &ldquo;...and no one is there to hear it, does it make a sound?&rdquo;
      p.rfcx-body
        span
          | These days, statistically speaking, when a tree falls in the forest, there's usually  somebody there to hear itâ€”the people that cut it down. With <em>Rainforest Connection</em> technology, we can finally rewrite this ancient adage, to read:
      p.rfcx-body
        span.italic
          | &ldquo;If a tree falls in the forest, and no one is there to hear it, <b>you</b> still can. And so can the world.&rdquo;


    div.span8
      div.screen-container(onClick="showHelpBubbles();")
        img.screen-img(src="#{rfcx_cdn}/img/about/screen-trans.560.png?v=#{app_version}")
        img.screen-bg(src="#{rfcx_cdn}/img/about/screen-bg.511.jpg?v=#{app_version}")
        div.roadgeek.hint--rounded.hint--bounce.hint--error.hint--top.alert-help(data-hint="HELP!", style="left:20%;top:25%;")
        div.roadgeek.hint--rounded.hint--bounce.hint--error.hint--top.alert-help(data-hint="HELP!", style="left:84%;top:33%;")
        div.roadgeek.hint--rounded.hint--bounce.hint--error.hint--top.alert-help(data-hint="HELP!", style="left:21%;top:55%;")
        div.roadgeek.hint--rounded.hint--bounce.hint--error.hint--top.alert-help(data-hint="HELP!", style="left:59%;top:60%;")
        div.roadgeek.hint--rounded.hint--bounce.hint--error.hint--top.alert-help(data-hint="HELP!", style="left:44%;top:30%;")
        div.roadgeek.hint--rounded.hint--bounce.hint--error.hint--top.alert-help(data-hint="HELP!", style="left:68%;top:24%;")

  div.row-fluid.rfcx-row-gradient.rfcx-row.rfcx-row-about-2
    div.span6
      img.trash-img(src="#{rfcx_cdn}/img/about/phone-trash-side.380.png?v=#{app_version}")
    div.span6
      p.roadgeek.rfcx-header
        | Turning old phones
        br
        | into forest guardians
      img.trash-img-mobile(src="#{rfcx_cdn}/img/about/phone-trash-side.380.png?v=#{app_version}")
      p.rfcx-body
        span
          | Why use old, recycled smartphones to guard the rainforest?
          br
          | Because it's simple, inexpensive and it works. 
      p.rfcx-body
        span
          | Smartphones are arguably the most efficient, advanced, and well-understood computers available on the market today, and each year, more than 150 million phones are discarded <a target="_blank" href="http://www.electronicstakeback.com/wp-content/uploads/Facts_and_Figures_on_EWaste_and_Recycling.pdf">in the United States alone</a>.
          br
          | <span class="italic">Rainforest Connection</span> can take this "trash" and put it to use immediately.
      p.rfcx-body
        span
          | Today, even earth's most remote forested areas have solid, reliable wireless telecommunications infrastructure. Rather than start from scratch, <span class="italic">Rainforest Connection</span> is already able to leverage this infrastructure from the start to protect the world's most threatened forests.

  div.row-fluid.rfcx-row-gradient.rfcx-row.rfcx-row-about-3
    div.span4
      p.roadgeek.rfcx-header= "Where do we start?"
      p.rfcx-body
        | The <span class="italic">Rainforest Connection</span> system works, and we've now <a href="video" target="_blank">proven it in the field</a> in Sumatra against actual illegal logging operations. Now we need to expand by putting the next generation of devices into <b>three more reserves</b> in the rainforests of Indonesia, the Amazon and Africa.
      p.rfcx-body
        | These three latest pilot projects will help to prove that the system can operate on <b>a global scale, in any forest, anywhere</b>.
      p.rfcx-body.rfcx-body-full
        | This requires funding and strong on-the-ground partnerships with local communities, indigenous partners and organizations that are committed to responding to logging alerts in real-time. We know that <span class="italic">Rainforest Connection</span> can help turn the tide of environmental crisis, but <a href="get_involved">we need your help</a> to make it a reality.
    div.span8
      div.rfcx-crnr-5.nopin.map-cropper
        img.map-frame(src="#{rfcx_cdn}/img/about/iphone5-black-bg.690.png?v=#{app_version}")
        div.map-cropper-internal
          div#map-container
          div.map-cover

  div.row-fluid.rfcx-row-gradient.rfcx-row.rfcx-row-sctn-join
    div.span7
      a#get_involved
      p.roadgeek.rfcx-header= "Help silence the chainsaws. Join us."
      p.rfcx-body
        div.stopsign-mobile
          img(src="#{rfcx_cdn}/img/intro/stopsign.358.png?v=#{app_version}")

        form.rfcx-form#mc-embedded-subscribe-form(name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form", target="_blank", action="https://rfcx.us7.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=c424f3e330b7fd5c41da1f891&amp;id=d040c73f65", method="post")

          span.rfcx-body
            span
              | Please <span class="bold">Like & Follow Us</span> 
              br.mobile-only
              | On Facebook, Twitter and Google+.
          
          div.social-follow-containers
            div.social-follow-container
              div.social-follow-item.fb-follow(data-width="300", data-show-faces="false", data-href="https://www.facebook.com/RainforestCx")
            div.social-follow-container
              a.social-follow-item.twitter-follow-button(data-show-count="true", href="https://twitter.com/RainforestCx")= "Follow @RainforestCx"
            div.social-follow-container
              div.social-follow-item.g-follow(data-height="24", data-href="//plus.google.com/+RfcxOrg", data-rel="publisher")


          div.control-group
            span.rfcx-body
              span
              | Stay informed by signing up for our <span class="bold">email newsletter.</span>
            br
            div.controls
              div.input-append
                input.input-large.email#mce-EMAIL(type='text', data-type='email', id='email', name='EMAIL', placeholder='Your email', required)
                a.btn.btn-success= "Sign up"

    div.span5
      img.stopsign(src="#{rfcx_cdn}/img/intro/stopsign.358.png?v=#{app_version}")